        "content": "<p>Out of curiosity, I went to check how mathlib proved this, and it turns out it doesn't have it? Looks like it is not so important as I thought <span aria-label=\"sweat smile\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f605\" role=\"img\" title=\"sweat smile\">:sweat_smile:</span> </p>\n<p>But mathlib does have a proof of the continuity of the sinc function <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Trigonometric/Sinc.html#Real.continuous_sinc\">Real.continuous_sinc</a>, from which one can easily derive the limit</p>",
